      "message": "Verify Existence Of All Sections In Firmware Page BIOS check is unconditional on current UI\n\nThe comment says BIOS is optional (config-dependent), but the code asserts it unconditionally with Page Should Contain BIOS. This will fail on current-UI systems without BIOS firmware support.\n\n```\nELSE\n    Page Should Contain  BMC\n    # BIOS section is present only on systems with Host firmware support.\n    ${has_bios}\u003d  Run Keyword And Return Status  Page Should Contain  BIOS\n    Log  BIOS section present: ${has_bios}\n```\n\nAligns the code with the stated intent in the documentation comment, preventing false failures on BMC-only systems.",
