      "writtenOn": "2026-07-13T08:35:45Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Run And Return Rc is deprecated — use Run Process or ${rc} ${out}\u003d Run And Return Rc And Output\n\nRun And Return Rc is a deprecated OperatingSystem library keyword. The modern replacement is Run Process (from the Process library) which provides return code, stdout, and stderr.\n\n```\n${result}\u003d  Run Process  tar  -xf  ${IMAGE_FILE_PATH}  -C  ${fw_verify_dir}/\nShould Be Equal As Integers  ${result.rc}  0\n...  msg\u003dFailed to extract firmware tar: ${IMAGE_FILE_PATH}\n```\n\nRun And Return Rc and Run are OperatingSystem library keywords that have been superseded by the Process library in Robot Framework. Using the modern API avoids deprecation warnings and is more portable",
      "revId": "82b61dd4e89794a7198981fc6cb8f841261555b7",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
    },
